    "description": "X Racing 不仅仅是赛道赛车，它还是一款互动动作游戏，拥有开放的世界和故事情节、精美的图形和酷炫的汽车、不同的游戏模式和在线游戏！<br><br><strong>物理学：</strong><br>汽车的物理性能和行为处于良好水平！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2160430/extras/4c61822e207b845842611f311859a59f.poster.avif?t=1703161753\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2160430/extras/4c61822e207b845842611f311859a59f.webm?t=1703161753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2160430/extras/4c61822e207b845842611f311859a59f.mp4?t=1703161753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>伤害系统：</strong><br>游戏有一个很好的汽车损坏系统，可以让你几乎把车毁得面目全非<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2160430/extras/7a1fee2336d0a852ba369ef3157a6a48.poster.avif?t=1703161753\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2160430/extras/7a1fee2336d0a852ba369ef3157a6a48.webm?t=1703161753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2160430/extras/7a1fee2336d0a852ba369ef3157a6a48.mp4?t=1703161753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>车辆：</strong><br>我们提请您注意从小型汽车到跑车的各种类型的交通工具。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2160430/extras/9a0885076141586d63bbe3becae9dae7.poster.avif?t=1703161753\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2160430/extras/9a0885076141586d63bbe3becae9dae7.webm?t=1703161753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2160430/extras/9a0885076141586d63bbe3becae9dae7.mp4?t=1703161753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>自定义你的车：</strong><br>在车库里，您有机会为自己定制汽车，升级发动机、操控和刹车，以及安装和配置各种系统，如（ABS、ESP、牵引控制、车轮驱动等）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2160430/extras/dcfddc7fa9faf5c0008891ea1f979d47.poster.avif?t=1703161753\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2160430/extras/dcfddc7fa9faf5c0008891ea1f979d47.webm?t=1703161753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2160430/extras/dcfddc7fa9faf5c0008891ea1f979d47.mp4?t=1703161753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>环境：</strong><br>在游戏中，您将可以通过开放世界、交通和 NPC 进入从山区、沙漠、高速公路到城市发展的各个级别<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2160430/extras/14000215b2ea3eaa6f9066f7d15ec08a.poster.avif?t=1703161753\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2160430/extras/14000215b2ea3eaa6f9066f7d15ec08a.webm?t=1703161753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2160430/extras/14000215b2ea3eaa6f9066f7d15ec08a.mp4?t=1703161753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>游戏模式：</strong><br><br>Arena (Derby) - 通过打破他的车来击败敌人！<br><br>最高速度 - 尽可能快地在高速公路上加速，您可以从汽车中挤出并到达目的地<br><br>检查点 - 以最短的方式到达该点<br><br>故事 - 游戏中的故事情节",
